liveBlogPostPrepared.plaintext: We've got our selves a ball guys, gals and NB pals. Jordan Riki was brought down by Jarome Luai, Herbie Farnworth was stopped by Dylan Edwards, but they couldn't stop Tom Flegler on the bullocking run at the left post. They came close though. liveBlogPostPrepared.title: TOM FLEGLER IS IN UNDER THE POSTS!

children.content: We've got our selves a ball guys, gals and NB pals.

Jordan Riki was brought down by Jarome Luai, Herbie Farnworth was stopped by Dylan Edwards, but they couldn't stop Tom Flegler on the bullocking run at the left post. They came close though. Isaah Yeo did everything but stop him, but the banana farmer caught enough of the line with the ball off the short ball from Tyson Smoothy.
Adam Reynolds converts and it's 8-6 with 14 seconds left in the half.

liveBlogPostPrepared.plaintext: The Broncos fullback scooped up a grubber and spotted a broken defensive line in front of him and got greedy, zooming across field and getting launched back into the in-goal by Brian To'o. The initial decision to go crossfield was risky, but once he got clipped he needed to stay down. Trying to get back up allowed To'o to take him back. And the short dropout is out on the full. Cleary pots the penalty goal from right in front. Penrith leads 8-0.
liveBlogPostPrepared.title: 28' Huge error from Walsh leads to two points for Penrith

children.content: More often than not it comes off for Reece Walsh, but that was a bad play.
The Broncos fullback scooped up a grubber and spotted a broken defensive line in front of him and got greedy, zooming across field and getting launched back into the in-goal by Brian To'o.
The initial decision to go crossfield was risky, but once he got clipped he needed to stay down. Trying to get back up allowed To'o to take him back.
And the short dropout is out on the full.
Cleary pots the penalty goal from right in front. Penrith leads 8-0.

liveBlogPostPrepared.plaintext: Brisbane's captain was dragged down in a tackle by Scott Sorensen and twisted awkwardly. He could've done his knee or ankle, but it looks like he's holding at his left hip. Huge moment. He's going to play on, but his mobility will be seriously lessened.
liveBlogPostPrepared.title: 25' Adam Reynolds is down injured
